Package: scAlign
Type: Package
Title: scAlign: scAlign: Single-cell clonal alignment for integrating scRNA-seq and scDNA-seq from the same specimen.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Xiangqi", "Bai", email = "xiangqi@stanford.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <xiangqi@stanford.edu>
Description: The scAlign package provides subclone assignment of scRNA-seq data to scDNA-seq subclones. It enables the construction of subclonal architecture using scDNA-seq, characterizes subclonal large-scale CNVs, and integrates paired scRNA-seq gene expression data and assign transcriptomes to subclones through gene dosage effects. 
